item.description:

[quote=“Miss Silabsoft, post:17, topic:526457”]Silabsoft’s naming guide!

  1. you can never have too many X’s but remember what you put on the front has to match on the back xxxXsilabsoftXxxx
  2. keywords such as “swag” “420” “blaze” “weed” instantly attract players.
  3. always use “scape” somewhere in the name
  4. nothing boosts your ego like naming the server after yourself
  5. when using a server with a higher revision of 317 make sure to call it a 317 server with customs it gives you credit for programming all that extra content.

copyright 2013 Silabsoft do not post on other websites has antileech![/quote]
